Drupal installation made easy. Process:
1. Downloads or detects drupal, unpacks it
2. Downloads libraries
3. Downloads modules (Needs improvement)
4. Setup installation profiles (Manual)

===============================================

16-May-2012, ver. 0.0.5
A. Drupal updates
- Libraries updated: CSS3Pie 5 beta to 1.0.0
- Module updates: webform, pathauto, token
B. Code updates:
- Generic URL when redirecting from index.php

===============================================

08-May-2012, ver. 0.0.3
A. Reference to Drupal version is generic now apart from default function parameter values
B. Updates:
- Core update 7.12 to 7.14
- Libraries updated: CKEditor 3.6.2 to 3.6.3
- Module updates: CSS3PIE, AdminMenu, Migrate & Backup, CKEditor, entity (1.0-rc1 to 1.0-rc2)
- Modules added: FontYourFace, Views Slideshow, Omega Theme Modules (Context, Delta, Omega Tools), Devel, Features, Entity, Override node options
C. Update to static instalation profile

